<body>
Reports the following JPA specification errors:<br/>
<ul>
  <li>Entity listener classes without public no-argument constructors</li>
  <li>Entity listener methods with incorrect signatures</li>
</ul><br/>

<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code lang="java">
  @Entity
  @EntityListeners(value = JavaEntityListener.class)
  class JavaEntity { ... }

  class JavaEntityListener {

    @PostLoad
    void postLoad(String parameter) { ... } // Error: method 'postLoad' should take parameter of type 'Object' here
  }
</code></pre>
</body>
